(21, 'Castify – Audio Podcast Theme', 'Castify-babiato-@TingTung', 'castify-audio', 'https://www.closecrowds.com/wp-admin/post.php?post=6818&action=edit', '/downloads/castify-audio-podcast-theme/', 'https://closecrowds.com/themes/?theme=castify-audio', 'https://elements.envato.com/castify-audio-podcast-elementor-template-kit-8DMCMFR', 'https://templatekit.jegtheme.com/castify/', 15, 'Audio,Blog,Comedian,Elementor,Entertainment,Episode,Influencers,Multimedia,Music,Player,Podcast,Radio,Series,Storyteller,Video Podcast,', '', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1KVxcbWdvvcBZ2u8V41g1cd0z9aM214__/view?usp=sharing', '<p>Castify is a modern Elementor Theme well-designed to promote your podcast shows. This template can be used by individuals and teams or companies, for example, comedians, storytellers, influencers, celebrities, radio networks, etc.</p>\r\n<p>Provide a better presentation of your podcast shows with this stunning Theme with a beautiful and unique design with a 100% responsive layout, retina-ready, and without a single line of coding!</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Using Free Plugins (Elementor Pro is not required)</li>\r\n    <li>Modern &amp; Clean Design</li>\r\n    <li>16+ Ready to use templates</li>\r\n    <li>Fully Responsive Layout</li>\r\n    <li>Retina Ready</li>\r\n    <li>Fully Customizable</li>\r\n    <li>Cross Browser Compatibility: Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Opera</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>Instruction</h2>\r\n<h3>How to Use Themes:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Install and Activate the \"Envato Elements\" plugin from Plugins &gt; Add New in WordPress</li>\r\n 	<li>Download your themes file and Do not unzip</li>\r\n 	<li>In WordPress, go to Elements &gt; Installed themes and click <strong>Upload Theme Zip File</strong>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6132\" src=\"https://www.closecrowds.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-on-2021-02-15-at-15_58_20-277x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"277\" height=\"300\"></li>\r\n 	<li>Check for the orange banner at the top and click Install Requirements to load any plugins the themes uses\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6133\" src=\"https://www.closecrowds.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screen-Shot-2020-05-12-at-2.29.56-pm-300x137.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"137\"></li>\r\n 	<li>Click import on the Global Kit Styles first</li>\r\n 	<li>Click Import on one template at a time. These are stored in Elementor under Templates &gt; Saved Templates.</li>\r\n 	<li>Go to Pages and create a new page and click Edit with Elementor</li>\r\n 	<li>Click the gear icon at lower-left of the builder to view page settings and choose Elementor Full Width and hide page title\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6134\" src=\"https://www.closecrowds.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/dc35b439-1f58-4130-5613-003f62c7c6f4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"286\" height=\"166\"></li>\r\n 	<li>Click the gray folder icon to access My Templates tab and then Import the page you like to customize.\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6135\" src=\"https://www.closecrowds.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/32d2168d-2706-4c8a-66e7-41376c273a1d-300x158.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"158\">\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6136\" src=\"https://www.closecrowds.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Annotation-on-2021-08-13-at-12-23-52-300x82.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"82\"></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nIf you have Elementor Pro, headers and footers may be customized by clicking the menu icon at top-left of the builder and choosing Theme Builder.\r\n<h3>Setup Global Header and Footer in ElementsKit</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Import the header and footer template</li>\r\n 	<li>Go to ElementsKit &gt; Header Footer and click Add New (if prompted with a wizard, you may click Next through it without taking any action)</li>\r\n 	<li>Title the header, leave Entire Site selected and toggle Activation to On</li>\r\n 	<li>Click the gray Edit Content button to load the builder</li>\r\n 	<li>Click the gray folder icon and select the header template to import, select your menu in the nav element and click Update.</li>\r\n 	<li>Repeat for Footer</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Help &amp; Support</h3>\r\nThese instructions are for those of you who just want to download themes and install them yourself. Our basic service includes installing it to your domain and hosting. So please order our basic service and we will install it for you.', 'array(\r\n        \"id\" 		 => \"Castify-Audio\",\r\n        \"url\" 		 => \"https://templatekit.jegtheme.com/castify/\",\r\n        \"purchase\" 	 => \"/downloads/castify-audio-podcast-theme/\",\r\n        \"responsive\" => \"yes\",\r\n        \"type\"       => \"wordpress\",\r\n        \"thumb\"      => \"\"\r\n    ),', 'ON', NULL, 1),
